                            <comment id="16507425" author="rhauch" created="Sun, 10 Jun 2018 15:40:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The KIP-285 changes appear to be bringing in &lt;tt&gt;javax.ws.rs.core.Configurable&lt;/tt&gt;, but rather than just bringing in the WS-RS API library (e.g., &lt;tt&gt;javax.ws.rs:javax.ws.rs-api:jar:2.1:compile&lt;/tt&gt;) it is bringing in all of Jersey.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We either need to include only the API JAR(s) that is / are necessary, or we need to re-evaluate whether the Connect API should expose that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
